## Rules

**Shared rules live in `CONSTITUTION.md`; stack rules live in `constitutions/<area>.md`.** Read
the root file always, and the area file for whatever member you are in. On conflict, the area
file narrows within its stack; the root governs everything shared. One home per rule, no drift.
